author: Guy Davies
title: UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson tests positive for coronavirus
description: UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson tests positive for coronavirus and will self-isolate for 14 days.
content:
LONDON -- 
The prime minister of the U.K. Boris Johnson has tested positive for coronavirus after developing mild symptoms.
